name: BaaBaablacksheepIndianrhyme
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: black sheep
des:
Baa, baa, black sheep
Have you any wool?
Yes sir, yes sir, three bags full.
One for the master,
And one for the dame,
And one for the little boy
Who lives down the lane.

This is a popular and famous Indian rhyme that plays baba black sheep.

Usage:
User: Alexa, open black sheep
Alexa: Starting baba black sheep, you can say start or begin to start the audio player
User: Begin
Alexa: Plays the rhyme

You can also say,
Alexa, next
Alexa, previous 
Alexa, pause
Alexa, stop
Alexa, resume
Alexa, shuffle
for respective tasks.

The Baba black sheep rhyme plays English audio which makes it suitable for English-speaking and listening users.

We hope you love it.
